   <conbody>
      <conbodydiv class="- topic/bodydiv concept/conbodydiv ">
         <section class="- topic/section ">
            <p class="- topic/p ">As an option it is possible to select analog instruments
for measuring certain values. There are available instruments for
both AC and DC.</p>
            <p class="- topic/p ">It is also possible to include other options
on the outside of the door.</p>
            <note class="- topic/note "> Please refer to the <i class="+ topic/ph hi-d/i ">Single
Line Diagram</i> of the system for the reference designator and exact
position.</note>
         </section>
